OL,3,C'Five basic failures' at hospital
OL,4,Cwhere Lucy Letby worked, inquiry told
OL,6,FPeter Skelton KC said there were "five
OL,7,Fbasic failures which occurred right
OL,8,Ffrom the start and which continued for
OL,9,Fthe next two years".
OL,11,F"The first failure was to conduct
OL,12,Fswift, careful and methodical
OL,13,Finvestigations into why each of the
OL,14,Fdeaths occurred and whether there were
OL,15,Fconnections between the deaths."He
OL,16,Fadded: "That was a major and
OL,17,Fcatastrophic failure."
