OL,6,FMr Skelton said it meant vital
OL,7,Finformation was overlooked, with
OL,8,F"fatal consequences" for other
OL,9,Fchildren.
OL,11,FHe said the cluster of deaths and
OL,12,Fcollapses should have been escalated
OL,13,Fto senior management within the
OL,14,Fhospital trust immediately, so they
OL,15,Fcould have overseen investigations.
