OL,3,C'Five basic failures' at hospital
OL,4,Cwhere Lucy Letby worked, inquiry told
OL,6,FThe barrister said a report into
OL,7,FBeverley Allitt, a nurse who killed
OL,8,Fchildren at Grantham Hospital,
OL,9,FLincolnshire, in 1991, sought to
OL,10,Fensure that healthcare staff were
OL,11,Fprepared to keep their minds open to
OL,12,Fthe possibility of criminal conduct.
OL,14,FAs well as the Allitt case, Mr Skelton
OL,15,Fsaid that in May 2015, just before
OL,16,FLetby's crimes began, nurse Victorino
OL,17,FChua was sentenced for murdering
OL,18,Fpatients at Stepping Hill Hospital.
