OL,3,C'Five basic failures' at hospital
OL,4,Cwhere Lucy Letby worked, inquiry told
OL,6,FHe told the inquiry the fifth failure
OL,7,Fwas not to inform the families that
OL,8,Fthe deaths were being investigated
OL,9,Fwith a view to finding out why they
OL,10,Foccurred.Mr Skelton said: "You will
OL,11,Fhear from some of the parents over the
OL,12,Fnext few weeks about how they were
OL,13,Fkept in the dark about the collapses
OL,14,Fof the babies and the concerns and
OL,15,Finvestigations that were being
OL,16,Fundertaken into their babies' deaths."
OL,18,FHe said the failings were made "all
OL,19,Fthe more indefensible" by the increase
OL,20,Fin numbers of neonatal deaths.
