OL,3,C'Five basic failures' at hospital
OL,4,Cwhere Lucy Letby worked, inquiry told
OL,6,FLetby, from Hereford, is serving 15
OL,7,Fwhole-life orders after she was
OL,8,Fconvicted at Manchester Crown Court of
OL,9,Fmurdering seven infants and attempting
OL,10,Fto murder seven others, with two
OL,11,Fattempts on one of her victims,
OL,12,Fbetween June 2015 and June 2016.
OL,14,FThe inquiry, chaired by Lady Justice
OL,15,FThirlwall, is expected to sit until
OL,16,Fearly 2025, with findings published by
OL,17,Flate autumn of that year. A court
OL,18,Forder prohibits reporting of the
OL,19,Fidentities of the surviving and dead
OL,20,Fchildren involved in the case.
